All Classes

Class Description
InvalidSequenceException
Thrown to notify classes that a password has more than two characters in sequence
LengthException
Thrown to notify classes that a password does not exceed the length requirement, in this case being six characters
NoDigitException
Thrown to notify classes that a password does not have any digits
NoLowerAlphaException
Thrown to notify classes that a password does not have a lowercase character
NoSpecialCharacterException
Thrown to notify other classes that a password does not have a special character
NoUpperAlphaException
Thrown to notify other classes that a password does not have an uppercase character
PasswordCheckerUtility
Utility class for checking if a password conforms to certain requirements to ensure security
UnmatchedException
Thrown to notify that two passwords do not match
WeakPasswordException
Thrown to notify that a password is valid, but could contain more characters for security
